 There’s currently pandemonium in Ikorodu area of Lagos State following the reported fatal shooting of a soldier, identified simply as Saheed, by a police officer. It was gathered that tragic incident occurred at Odogunyan bustop on Wednesday evening, February 15, 2023. ALSO READ: Man caught despite disguising self as a sheep to escape prison Details of the incident are still sketchy as at time filling this report, but multiple reports claim there’s heavy military presence in the area, and gunshots are being heard. A police station and vehicles have been reportedly set ablaze by angry soldiers. 